{"word":"H539 - אָמַן - ʼâman - aw-man' - Hence","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אָמַן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>ʼâman"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>aw-man'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Hence"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"உண்மையுள்ளவனாயிரு, ஸ்திரப்பட்டிரு. உறுதியாயிரு, நிலையாயிரு, மெய்யென்று விளங்கு, நிலைவரப்பட்டிரு, விசுவாசி, நம்பிக்கையுள்ளவனாயிரு, நம்பு, சத்தியமாயிரு, நிச்சயமாயிரு, அஞ்சாமலிரு, துணிகரங்கொள்ளு - வினைச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to support, to confirm, to be faithful"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"to support, to confirm, to be faithful, to uphold, tonourish"},{"paragraph":"1) foster father (a substantive)"},{"paragraph":"2) foster mother, nurse"},{"paragraph":"3) pillars, supporters of the door"},{"paragraph":"b) (Niphal)"},{"paragraph":"to be established, to be faithful, to be carried, to make firm"},{"paragraph":"1) to be carried by a nurse"},{"paragraph":"2) to made firm, to be sure, to be lasting"},{"paragraph":"3) confirmed, established, sure"},{"paragraph":"4) verified, confirmed"},{"paragraph":"5) reliable, faithful, trusty"},{"paragraph":"C) (Hiphil)"},{"paragraph":"to stand firm, to trust, to be certain, to believe in"},{"paragraph":"1) to stand firm"},{"paragraph":"2) to trust, to believe"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly to <i>build up</i> or <i>support</i>; to <i>foster</i> as a parent or nurse; figuratively to <i>render</i> (or <i>be</i>) <i>firm</i> or faithful, to <i>trust</i> or believe, to be <i>permanent</i> or quiet; morally to <i>be true</i> or certain; once (in Isa 30:21; by interchange for <a href=\"#/H541 - אָמַן - ʼâman - aw-man'/541\">H541</a>) to <i>go to the right hand: - </i>hence assurance, believe, bring up, establish, + fail, be faithful (of long continuance, stedfast, sure, surely, trusty, verified), nurse, (-ing father), (put), trust, turn to the right."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1968 - הֵימָן - Hêymân - hay-mawn'/1968\">H1968</a>, <a href=\"#/H4104 - מְהוּמָן - Mᵉhûwmân - meh-hoo-mawn'/4104\">H4104</a>, <a href=\"#/H525 - אָמֹון - ʼâmôwn - aw-mone'/525\">H525</a>, <a href=\"#/H526 - אָמֹון - ʼÂmôwn - aw-mone'/526\">H526</a>, <a href=\"#/H527 - אָמֹון - ʼâmôwn - aw-mone'/527\">H527</a>, <a href=\"#/H529 - אֵמוּן - ʼêmûwn - ay-moon'/529\">H529</a>, <a href=\"#/H530 - אֱמוּנָה - ʼĕmûwnâh - em-oo-naw'/530\">H530</a>, <a href=\"#/H539 - אָמַן - ʼâman - aw-man'/539\">H539</a>, <a href=\"#/H542 - אָמָן - ʼâmân - aw-mawn'/542\">H542</a>, <a href=\"#/H543 - אָמֵן - ʼâmên - aw-mane'/543\">H543</a>, <a href=\"#/H544 - אֹמֶן - ʼômen - oh-men'/544\">H544</a>, <a href=\"#/H545 - אׇמְנָה - ʼomnâh - om-naw'/545\">H545</a>, <a href=\"#/H546 - אׇמְנָה - ʼomnâh - om-naw'/546\">H546</a>, <a href=\"#/H547 - אֹמְנָה - ʼômᵉnâh - om-me-naw'/547\">H547</a>, <a href=\"#/H548 - אֲמָנָה - ʼămânâh - am-aw-naw'/548\">H548</a>, <a href=\"#/H549 - אֲמָנָה - ʼĂmânâh - am-aw-naw'/549\">H549</a>, <a href=\"#/H550 - אַמְנֹון - ʼAmnôwn - am-nohn'/550\">H550</a>, <a href=\"#/H551 - אׇמְנָם - ʼomnâm - om-nawm'/551\">H551</a>, <a href=\"#/H552 - אֻמְנָם - ʼumnâm - oom-nawm'/552\">H552</a>, <a href=\"#/H571 - אֶמֶת - ʼemeth - eh'-meth/571\">H571</a>, <a href=\"#/H573 - אֲמִתַּי - ʼĂmittay - am-it-tah'ee/573\">H573</a>, <a href=\"#/H71 - אֲבָנָה - ʼĂbânâh - ab-aw-naw'/71\">H71</a>"}]}